o Rovere]]''' | '''[[Maserati in motorsport|Maserati]] 6C-34''' | 21 | Fuel feed/valve? | 11 |- ! DNF | 28 | {{flagicon|ITA|1861}} '''[[Piero Dusio]]''' | '''Scuderia Subalpina''' | '''[[Maserati 8CM]]''' | 3 | Crash | 14 |- ! DNF | 6 | {{flagicon|DEU|1933}} '''[[Manfred von Brauchitsch]]''' | '''[[Daimler-Benz|Daimler-Benz AG]]''' | '''[[Mercedes-Benz W25]]K''' | 1 | Gearbox | 3 |- |colspan=8| Source:<ref name=kolumbus>{{cite web|url=http://www.kolumbus.fi/leif.snellman/gp3501.htm|title=VII GRAND PRIX DE MONACO|publisher=kolumbus.fi|accessdate=3 October 2016}}</ref> |}
