{{Infobox cycling race | name = Azencross | current_event = | image = | image_caption = | date = December | region = [[Flemish Region]], [[Belgium]] | english = | localnames = | nickname = | discipline = Cyclo-cross | competition = [[BPost Bank Trophy]] | type = | organiser = | director = | first = {{start date|1984}} | number = 34 (as of 2017) | final = | firstwinner = {{flagathlete|[[Roland Liboton]]|BEL}} | mostwins = {{flagathlete|[[Sven Nys]]|BEL}} ''(6 wins)'' | mostrecent = {{flagathlete|[[Mathieu van der Poel]]|NED}} }} [[File:Zdeněk Štybar at the Azencross 2012.jpg|thumb|Zdeněk Štybar in the 2012 edition]] The '''Azencross''' is a [[cyclo-cross]] race held in [[Loenhout]] village, [[Wuustwezel]], [[Belgium]], which is part of the [[BPost Bank Trophy]].
