{{infobox country at games | NOC = BIR | NOCname = | games = Summer Olympics | year = 1980 | flagcaption = | oldcode = | website = | location = [[Moscow]] | competitors = 2 | sports = 2 | flagbearer = [[Myint Sann]] | rank = | gold = 0 | silver = 0 | bronze = 0 | officials = 1 | appearances = auto | app_begin_year = | app_end_year = | summerappearances = | winterappearances = | seealso = {{flagIOC|MYA}} (1992-) }}
'''[[Burma]]''' competed at the '''[[1980 Summer Olympics]]''' in [[Moscow]], [[Soviet Union|USSR]]. The South Asian nation returned the Olympic Games after missing the [[1976 Summer Olympics]].
