'''Club Aurora''' is a [[association football|football]] club from [[Cochabamba]], Bolivia, that plays in the [[Bolivian Primera División|División de Fútbol Profesional]], the top tier of Bolivian football. The club was founded May 27, 1935, and plays its home games at the [[Estadio Félix Capriles]].

