'''Raed Chabab Kouba''' ({{Lang-ar|رائد شباب القبة}}) known as '''RC Kouba''' or simply '''RCK''' for short, is an [[Algeria]]n [[Association football|football]] club based in [[Kouba, Algeria|Kouba]], a district of [[Algiers]]. The club was founded in 1945 and its colours are green and white. Their home stadium, [[Stade Omar Benhaddad]], has a capacity of some 10,000 spectators. The club is currently playing in the [[Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 2]].

